name: Original linocut print of three free black birds and flying birds
description:
This is one of several linocut prints I made inspired on my artist book Among Humans:

http://www.cassa-studio.com/project/artist-book-among-humans-2/?full=1

I got inspired to make the book and the prints from my daily terrace view. I see birds flying in unison during the day resting on my neighbors´ antennas making noises to attract other birds. 

This is number II on the series. The images are hand carved in linoleum and then printed on cotton paper with black ink. The three birds are cutouts and glued on the paper making a little relieve.

Paper size 18x18cms (7x7")

The frame is not included.

Thanks for visiting!

Cassandra

name: Mediterranean set of THREE linocut prints
description:
This is a set of prints I made inspired on Mediterranean tiles. I´ve been living in the Mediterranean coast for few years now and I´ve been falling for this kind of geometric patterns as facades, stairs and walls decorations. They are my latest inspiration and obsession :)

They are original prints from hand carved linoleum printed on cotton paper and glued on wood supports. The design was made by me as well as the prints and wood frames.
Each print tile has my logo on the back and it is signed. It also has little metal rings and a hem cord to hang.

Size: 6" x 6"
The price is for the THREE of them.

I hope you like them, they are pieces that can make any home or studio space more special with that Mediterranean-Summer touch. ;)

Thanks for visiting my shop!

Cassandra

name: Pocket size Moleskine notebooks with Pattern design.
description:
This Moleskine notebook is hand stamped with a rubber stamp designed by me. It also has very thing golden lines to add an elegant touch to the cover.
The pattern is inspired by organic shapes from nature.

The notebook available in the picture is blank inside but you can choose between blank, ruled or squared paper, whatever you fancy to write or sketch on.

Pocket size: 3.5" x 5.5" (9x14cm)
Acid free paper.
64 pages
Detachable pages: last 16
It also has a mini pocket on the back cover.

name: Colorful pattern, handmade linocut print "Kaleido I"
description:
This is an original print made from one linoleum repetitively hand printed on cotton paper. 

Size of cotton paper: 40cm x 40cm........15 3/4" x 15 3/4 "
Size of image: 36cm x36 cm........14"x14"

Ink: Speedball for linocuts
Frame not included
Original print, signed and dated. 

Thanks for looking!

Cassandra

name: Hanging print of an original linocut image of three free black birds.
description:
This is one linocut print I made inspired on my artist book "Among Humans".
